- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper specifically focuses on JavaScript frameworks, which are related to programming languages. 
- cs.SD (Software Development) is relevant as the paper discusses factors related to the efficiency and functionality of JSFs, which are important in software development. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is less likely but still possible as the paper may touch on the impact of JSFs on society and the role of developers in making decisions that affect users.
